	<li>
		We&#39;re thrilled to add two more people to our team this month: <a href="http://newtactics.us5.list-manage.com/track/click?u=acc46cd2cef604ae60bd5355b&amp;id=f29fcac2f6&amp;e=5808ddf12d" style="color:#336699;font-weight:normal;text-decoration:underline" target="_blank">Ruba Al Bream</a> will serve as the MENA Online Community Builder and <a href="http://newtactics.us5.list-manage.com/track/click?u=acc46cd2cef604ae60bd5355b&amp;id=8788a55a50&amp;e=5808ddf12d" style="color:#336699;font-weight:normal;text-decoration:underline" target="_blank">Ramy Raoof</a> will serve as our MENA Tactic Researcher.</li>


	<li>
